Methods

Connected to CFPB Consumer Complaint Database (2023) in Power BI
Built calculated measures comparing raw complaint counts against monetary relief rates and referral rates by state
Visualized company response distributions and resolution outcomes
Ranked companies by total complaint volume

Data Source
CFPB Consumer Complaint Database
https://www.consumerfinance.gov/data-research/consumer-complaints/
